import React from "react";
import { Box, Image } from "@chakra-ui/react";
import { Keyboard, Pagination, Navigation } from "swiper";
import { Swiper, SwiperSlide } from "swiper/react";

// carousel styles
import "swiper/css";

const Herocarousel = () => {
  return (
    <>
      <Box>
        <Swiper
          slidesPerView={1}
          spaceBetween={30}
          keyboard={{
            enabled: true,
          }}
          pagination={{
            clickable: true,
          }}
          navigation={true}
          modules={[Keyboard, Pagination, Navigation]}
          className="mySwiper"
        >
          <SwiperSlide>
            <Image
              src="https://api.unsplash.com/users/lukeskywalker/photos"
              alt="1"
            />
          </SwiperSlide>
          <SwiperSlide>
            <Image
              src="https://api.unsplash.com/users/lukeskywalker/photos"
              alt="2"
            />
          </SwiperSlide>
          <SwiperSlide>
            <Image
              src="https://api.unsplash.com/users/lukeskywalker/photos"
              alt="3"
            />
          </SwiperSlide>
          <SwiperSlide>
            <Image
              src="https://api.unsplash.com/users/lukeskywalker/photos"
              alt="4"
            />
          </SwiperSlide>
          <SwiperSlide>
            <Image
              src="https://api.unsplash.com/users/lukeskywalker/photos"
              alt="5"
            />
          </SwiperSlide>
          <SwiperSlide>
            <Image
              src="https://api.unsplash.com/users/lukeskywalker/photos"
              alt="6"
            />
          </SwiperSlide>
          <SwiperSlide>
            <Image
              src="https://api.unsplash.com/users/lukeskywalker/photos"
              alt="7"
            />
          </SwiperSlide>
          <SwiperSlide>
            <Image
              src="https://api.unsplash.com/users/lukeskywalker/photos"
              alt=""
            />
          </SwiperSlide>
          <SwiperSlide>
            <Image
              src="https://api.unsplash.com/users/lukeskywalker/photos"
              alt=""
            />
          </SwiperSlide>
        </Swiper>
      </Box>
    </>
  );
};

export default Herocarousel;
